Dialogue: Meow!
Ooh ooh! Ooh...ooh?
What in the hells is going on here!?
And here I thought monsters were on the loose...
Now then, what can I learn today?
Pumpkin pudding... It sounds simply marvelous!
That was a fearsome foe.
Who was that voidsent...?
Is that it?
Transformation, hmm? Ladies, I've a wonderful idea for our next concert!
Isn't it just fascinating?
What a peculiar festival.
So this is the measure of a keyward's power...
We weren't too late.
So long as she lives there is yet hope.
We've won!
Now we end this.
I sense a dreadful presence...
This does not bode well.
Does that...belong there?
Now, what do you think Mother would like?
Hmm...
I know! A treat we can enjoy as a family!
Hmm... How about a big cake?
Carrot juice protocols active.
I fear their levitation faculties are still developing...
Mimimimi!♪
Miii!
<burble> ...Mi?
Oh, I couldn't possibly. What if the Fighters need it?
Why did she refuse to listen? Why didn't I...
We're nearly to the summit. Let's keep moving.
...We should go, Ysayle. The summit awaits.
On your guard. Our work here is not yet done.
Are you all right, my friend?
We must hurry, ere the archbishop can make good his escape.
Shall I leave this fertilizer here?
Let the Citizens have this batch.
Fertilizer delivery!
You can stay─but tell no one.
A suitable location for meditation.
Quite. And we have much time.
Which thesis shall we obliterate?
Er...
Have a dip!
We must nourish them further. But how...
Relax. They are already pleasingly gelatinous.
This unit is but a tiny speck among the cosmos...
Flora identification requested.
This tree represents the world─us, its leaves.
<whirr> ...Interconnected units. As are we!
Come back here!
Perhaps Ra-la's is not the only blessing.
Still accounting for our differences, of course...
Not a bad idea.
I suppose we can try it your way.
Surface temperature: pleasing.
Instructive! <beep> <beep> <beep> <BWAAAAAA>
Pardon me─it appears I am experiencing an emotion...
Relaxation...achieved?
Downloading “ambling” add-on...
Share and share alike, I suppose.
...Please just take it.
The boldness of youth... This is well.
Grew these with my own two hands!
Just a little lick!
Vital signs optimal. Hatchlings will grow large and robust.
<yawn> Another beautiful day in─ Oh dear.
<gasp> It's the underworld, yes, yes!
No, no, it must be a dream. Back to my jar...
Underworld catfish! Help, heeelp!
Soup! Soup! Soup!
Waiter! Another, please!
Mi-miii!
Mi mi mi mi...<screech>♪
<burble>
I can scarcely take another hop, ribbit...
Oh, for the time to pore over this collection...
Now then, where might Master Matoya's tome be?
The aether here is almost too much for my eyes.
So this is the closest point to the aetherial sea...
We've come for you, Minfilia...
I shan't soon forget this trial.
I gave my all. I pray it was enough...
The Ixal fought to the very last...
Tee hee hee! Go on, go on!
Watch it fidget! How adorable!
Tell me, do you like flowers?
Kweh, kweh!
Just how powerful are these ryu...?
Woooooo!
Yea! Yea, I say!
Mmmmmmuffin...
Let's add it to my list...
This looks fun!
This looks tasty!
How exciting!
How lovely!
Needs more carrots...
At least we have plenty in stock!
I could swear this was a whole cake last I checked...
Baked to perfection!
How sweet!
Not quite golden brown yet...
Am I allowed to play on this? Let's go with “yes”...
Where are they?
We're fully stocked!
I present...this!
It's very...this.
S-Snake! There's a snake amongst the eggs!

My precious Archon egg...
They just...took it...

Agh, my gift! Sunk to the bottom...
Those blasted sylphs!
N-No more pranks... Cease this madness, I beg of you...
Thanks to you, I was able to focus on the data collection.
I believe we may declare this foray a success!
Gods, I'm exhausted. What's a woman have to do to get a bloody drink?
Ah, Madam Rowena. A pleasure, as always.
Why, hello there. Won't you show me around your fine...establishment?
Those muscles... They're like tree trunks...
What have we here? A craftsman after my own heart...
Fascinating... A complex interplay between light and the wood's natural form.
Can you catch us, kupo?
So long as there's drink, I can manage...
One moment poor as a pauper, the next rich as a king! Ah, what a magical place!
My readers would be very interested to know what items are on offer.
It's a good thing we found your mother, isn't it?
Thank you, mister! Thank you!
This young lad was a great help in the search.
The colors of summer should lend themselves splendidly to new garments.
We're here to glean inspiration for Tataru Taru's Boutique!
The sea here looks so different than in Thavnair... I could stare at it forever!
Oh, thank the gods Khloe is safe...
Of course not, T'kebbe! The savior was amazing!
You weren't scared, Khloe?
We'll catch our fortunes soon enough, I can feel it!
I heard tell there's fish around here that'll fetch a whole sack of gil.
Kweh! Kweh!
Ungh... What the─!?
You almost have it, my lord!
Guess your blue blood's not worth much here, eh?
No one else saw that... Aye, no one else...
I'm so full of desserts... And so cold...
I hear that a master of making confectionaries has come to enjoy the festivities.
Everyone here's having so much fun!
If only the moon had something like this...
That's quite a few bombs. We may soon need a resupply...
Hehehe... Worry not. I have brought enough for many, many booms─blasts, bangs, booms!
Ungh... I can't do any better than this...?
You can do it! Go, go!
I believe in you!
Yum yum!
I won't doubt myself any longer!
Don't worry!
When it comes to water...
...We're filled to the brim!
This might be beyond me...
One step at a time...
So many bombs! Eeek!
Easy does it...
Come visit the memorial space when you have a moment!
Glub...glub...glub...!
Ahhh... Now that's refreshing!
Come on... Just a little further...
Quit faking or you'll distract the savior from real heroics!
I can do this... Maybe.
I can't fall...not again!
Every failure just makes you stronger! Show us what you're made of!
If trouble comes knocking, the Sunshine Savior will scare it off!
Even if it's a shark that's thiiis big!
H-Hey! Don't tempt fate like that!
What scent drew that shark here, I wonder?
Someone said there's a breathtaking vista next to the course.
Really!? Promise we'll go later.
Welcome, welcome!
You did well to make it here!
Such courage! Such grace!
That's our savior?
Aye, it takes courage to wear something like that...
The only thing better than making desserts is watching people tumble into the sea.
Oh, to be a chocobo chick in a dragon costume...
How precious!
Sounds like it'll be smooth sailing for me this year!
Hm. Maybe I should get me own blessin'...
Why do you suppose they chose here for their lair?
Well, that was a challenge.
So goes yet another archfiend.
I've never seen a voidsent with such command over water.
That they could open so large a gate is troubling.
I feel your presence, Sister. Where are you?
What if we volunteer to distribute eggs?
Time to transform these eggs into adorable tonberries!
Does that make them...toneggies?
I do wish we could help somehow...
Well, what do you like to do?
I haven't the foggiest.
Why not try inventing a machine?
W-With wrenches!? Oooh...
Are you interested in cooking?
I do like to eat...
How about painting?
I don't have the talent. Or coordination...
Would you like to be on the radio?
Would I!?
Did you find a dream?
I found too many. Now I'm confused...
What a nice uniform you have!
Dreaming...
My dream is to wear one of those uniforms!
My dream is to have lunch at the cooking station!
My dream is to have a dream!
Aw...
I'll be back─with a proper dream!
I'm one of the Dreaming Ways now!
...I'm not certain that counts.
Hail, my best Way!
Mayhap I'll interview the Thornes while I have the chance...

The Little Ladies' Dance...
I never thought I'd see it...
If only Claudia were alive to see this...

Perhaps this festival's better
than I gave it credit for.
Mother, it's beautiful!
For this year's celebration...
We'll be distributing gorgeous fans to everyone!
Please give us just a moment to prepare!

Behold, Princess Edvya's
Little Ladies' Dance!
You are all welcome to join us!
There are enough fans for everyone!

Outfits that better highlight
the dance...color me intrigued!
What a cute dance!
Do you think I can do it too?
Of course, dear. Just take it one step at a time.
What sort of fans, I wonder?
Oooh, I can't wait!
I wonder what the Songbirds have planned...
How very elegant!
Perhaps I shall give it a try!
The Songbirds are amazing!

The day has come, my friends...
Pudding has evolved!
I want you to make pudding! The best pudding in this realm or any other!
These younglings are rooting for your success!
My, my, you're quite good at this!
I shall uncover this slippery secret!
The architect of this space is truly a master of his craft...
What frightful mind thought these up, kupo?
It's not that bad, kupo.
Oh, how can I possibly thank you!
Whoa! This isn't a closet at all!
I know this song!
White and blue! You're a miracle worker!
Maybe they'll read mine next!
My arms are getting tired...
Ready to go?
What took you so long?
I tripped! Tail over teakettle, straight into a creation station...
I'll climb you good!
Hyaaahhh! No one messes with a pirate!
Pace yerself!
Why, hello!
The sea's callin' to ye, ain't she?
I can't fall...not again!
Thus the legend is unmasked...
Of all the eerie things here, that was definitely the eeriest.
Now we can resume our voyage.
I cannot put this isle behind us soon enough...
Finally, we may breathe easy...
Such a ferocious bird that was.
We did it! We passed the trial!
Let us press on to the keep!
Be safe, my lord...
I'm only just limbering up!
I wonder how Lyse fares.
What now...?
He enjoyed this, the monster...
It's not over yet. Stay sharp.
There's no escape, Zenos!
I guess not all adults are bad people...
Yeah, we've still got a lot of growing up to do!
You're right... Maybe we should go on an adventure someday!
B-Be careful!
Actually, I have news of my own─I've earned a place in the interim government!
Did I tell you? I've started up my own business to support the town.
Such a pleasant breeze...
Would you just look at the stars...
Nothing pairs with curry better than a breathtaking performance.
So, the thing about spicy foods is...
Perhaps it's time to expand our spice trade...
Is there something you'd like to eat?
Ooh, the stew! Can you make it again?
Where do we go from here...
The contingent should be along any moment now...
Oh, he'll be delighted! Have you decided what to make?
Mother, I want to prepare supper for Father today!
Just try to relax, dear.
Will the medicine really help...?
Seems the geyser is just beyond.
Mayhap these waters are connected to the sea.
Had it been squid, we might have taken some for Estinien.
Nothing to it.
Did you hear?
I heard on the radio...
They're giving out candy at All Saints' Wake!
I'm going to stuff myself with pudding!
Me, too!
Is this what the guild's been buzzing about...?
I can't look!
A voidsent is close, I can smell it...
Of course, it could be something else...
To think there could be monsters lurking about...
Not surprising, considering the origins of this occasion...
I've heard he goes wild for cookies.
I'm scared, but I can't look away...
I know what you mean...
Quite the odd spectacle...
My brothers will love this.
I heard rumors of monsters about, but it turns out it was all part of the festivities.
Papa Gruff seems to be having so much fun!
Maybe being liked isn't so bad after all!
Thank goodness for warm meals...
The damage to the city is even more extensive than we thought...
What other materials might be reusable...?
Our ceruleum stores are in good shape of late.
What did you get for Starlight?
Let's all play together!
Witness the miracle of Starlight illusions!
So many lovely presents!
Not all gifts are gained with gil.
I wonder if the Ehcatl Nine would enjoy the Starlight Celebration...
What's 'e doin' 'ere, the blithe bastard!?
Is she here for celebration or assassination...?
What do we have here...?
Oh? What is it, Ojika?
Just a little bit longer!
Fascinating...
I-I saw you there, I assure you!

Why not take a short break?
I'd be happy to assist afterwards.
Come an' get yer Starlight presents!
Go on, then!
If Khloe gets a gift, Khloe's gonna write a whole page about it in her journal...
So many letters of gratitude...
I should write something too. Gods know I owe lots of people.
Do you have aught to report?
We must free the rest of our colleagues.
Pandæmonium's protective wards have been restored.
That Athena would build all this...
This isn't all she's left behind.
Where're the others?
They're hiding somewhere. Let's go find 'em!
How long before they find us, you think?
Well, they already know all the good hiding places...
When they do, we should all go to the beach!
Ooh, and then we can look at the stars until we fall asleep!
Piles upon piles of treasure... I can scarcely imagine how much there is.
Arenvald has gotten stronger, hasn't he?
To think that that monster used to be a man...
That there in the distance...
Please be safe, Alphinaud...
That dragon was as much mist as it was flesh.
Dragons at Allagan ruins are seldom a coincidence.
It seems we've thrown them back.
Is it over already?
Their teamwork was quite fearsome, I must allow.
That Hyper Hustle was incredible!
Pure fiction, beyond a doubt.
Zzz... Forward, brave hippo...
It's just as our listeners described!
Was there truly no other way?
He all but set his soul aflame...
It should not have come to this.
A bitter victory...
Did you get that feedback down?

Listeners...indignant...yet...
thrilled...
'Tis already quite impressive to behold.
Ook!
So it's temporarily constructed with wood.
Ah, such an invigorating breeze...
Ook, ook!
Oh, Etheirys...
Your beauty truly knows no bounds.
Forgive me, I was lost in thought.
I look forward to the bridge's completion.
Lord Golbez!
And Lord Durante too!
Hope is not yet lost!
Our saviors have returned!
Ka-pa-paaa!
These imps don't hold a candle to Senor Sabotender...!
Please, my darling, won't you let me take you to dinner?
Oh fine, if you insist...
So that's how you do it...
Here goes nothing...
M-Milady?
She'll make a fine emissary of love yet.
Emilie's giving it her all!
Imps! My buddies! My pals!
Well now, that we should visit this place at the same time...
All is well with the instrument, and I trust 'tis likewise with you.
Take care, my friend. Till next we meet.
Find anything yet?
Thank you for coming!
We hope you enjoy yourselves!
Next is the main attraction!
Little Ladies' Day is far from over!
It'll be eggcellent!
Things are just heating up!
Ulala! Look at me!
Such grace!
Yes, woo! Woo, I say!
Three cheers for the Beans!
I was mere ilms away from the crown... Ilms, I tell you!
There's always next time!
Woo! Woo-woo!
<plip>
Ah, of course... It seems the celebrations are underway.
And one! And two! And three! And four!
It's like you were born to hop!
Grandmother trained me in the yol dance!
A curious way to train...
